item.title: There's a Thousand Reason You'll Fail
item.description: There could potentiall be thousands of reasons that will cause me to fail big corporations stronger competitions corporations with huge investment funds But the strength given to all start ups and small players. Are the strength of speed and flexibility. We do not have the fear of losing our existing base or our existing schema, culture, whatever. Because we begin with nothing. Move fast. We can definitely move faster than giant corporations.
